                        <p>Five Fearless Predictions:</p>
<ol>
<li><p>Despite losing J.J. Redick and Shelden Williams, Duke reaches the Final Four for the first time since 2004.</p></li>
<li><p>Florida follows the Pittsburgh Steelers' lead and is terrible the year after winning it all.</p></li>
<li><p>Maryland wins the ACC Tournament.</p></li>
<li><p>Wichita State wins the NCAA Tournament.</p></li>
<li><p>Dick Vitale is fired.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>OK, maybe that last one is just wishful thinking.</p>

